{"tid":1404943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[召集愛國愛港朋友] 好撚驚聽日罷工出唔到深圳食酸菜魚","createTime":"2019-08-04T06:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:56:40.000Z","uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9192911c4803b5e1795d8bf5995b8fbb81849b36","tid":1404943,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"示威者佔路已經佔到熟哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時老龍屯工本身都塞車架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班人等到透唔到氣棄車去路透做CPR都唔使諗條路可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三條隧道一定唔多正常<br />\n<br />\n除咗圍巴士廠出唔到車外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人仲話要塞爆地鐵<br />\n<br />\n難聽講句港鐵每條線都有露天路段<br />\n平時孔明燈跌落東鐵線都死全條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有錫紙氫氣球都搞到中秋好掃興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍田至彩虹、荔景至葵興、杏花村至柴灣、東西馬鐵新界段&hellip;全部露天<br />\n屌你啲仆街暴徒成張錫面露營地蓆、成卷錫紙掉落去一定GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好講啲和理非仲話集體坐爆MTR，根本車尾燈都無撚得你見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個MTR系統整到星期二都唔知整唔整得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆你個街<br />\n聽日係咪已經冇方法可以出境，甚至出街<br />\n有冇人可以講啲可行出入方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集思廣益睇下可以點做<img src=\"/asse