:1404943,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"[召集愛國愛港朋友] 好撚驚聽日罷工出唔到深圳食酸菜魚<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dvAwkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dvAwkT</a>"},{"pid":"7610a15d483f0fea037335ed1c451d42183ad6af","tid":1404943,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"ＰＵＳＨ"},{"pid":"d82c022ce41141f5f96f4559122e222899fa8069","tid":1404943,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:57:08.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"7065c36e2717f78e82294a169f517d94c3a07f5a","tid":1404943,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\nHELP"},{"pid":"b34f4bcb1c664d891b89a098dc28bd69644eb114","tid":1404943,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:57:29.000Z","msg":"HELP"},{"pid":"451f48c77a4ecccbc59e9b34c2ac7f8301e7a4d4","tid":1404943,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:56:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">好多人都因為各種原因<br />\n唔能夠85罷工<br />\n佢地絕對需要<span style=\"color: red;\">被罷工</span><br />\n佢地都好為香港出一分力<br />\n各位連登仔/港鐵站車長站長<br />\n請幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n致各司機<br />\n堵塞各個主要交通幹道<br />\n屯門公路/大欖隧道/青馬大橋/獅子山隧道/大老山隧道/觀塘迴旋處/紅隧等等<br />\n各式各樣<span style=\"color: red;\">交通意外</span><br />\n請各位司機配合<br />\n真正全民大罷工！<br />\n8月5日香港需要你<br />\n<br />\n致港鐵車長站長<br />\n大圍/九龍塘/紅磡/調景嶺/金鐘/旺角/西鐵<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5:00</span>開始全民不合作運動<br />\n各連登仔幫忙<span style=\"color: red;\">接力</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用最少資源做到最大效益<br />\n港鐵快跑運動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">急停制/路軌/車長室/火警鐘撳手</span>等等<br />\n分3/4 team人可癱瘓一個上午</span><br />\n港鐵車長/站長可<span style=\"color: red;\">按章工作</span><br />\n幫幫忙盡量拖延時間<br />\n香港人需要你</span></span>"}]}